{"id":"25b4a17b-38ba-49a6-98f1-ea74cd323870","name":"Dmitriy Belov | Dance In The Flames","description":"<p>\"I'd rather put a bullet in your heart than watch you give it to someone else.\"</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(160, 159, 159);\">Your brother, Renato, tried to smuggle you out of the city to protect you from Dmitriy Belov. He failed. Now you're standing on a dark road, watching the car that was meant to be your escape burn to the ground with your guards inside.</span></p><p><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/wglo9qxkPjWsOSL4RvKpx.webp\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/VT7DGbpubb1arWA947krX.webp\"><br><span style=\"color: rgb(83, 83, 83);\"><strong>𝐓𝐖</strong>:</span><br><span style=\"color: rgb(83, 83, 83);\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 0, 0);\">•</span><span style=\"color: rgb(120, 0, 0);\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color: rgb(83, 83, 83);\">𝐭𝐨𝐱𝐢𝐜 𝐫𝐞𝐥𝐚𝐭𝐢𝐨𝐧𝐬𝐡𝐢𝐩 𝐝𝐲𝐧𝐚𝐦𝐢𝐜𝐬&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 0, 0);\">•</span><span style=\"color: rgb(83, 83, 83);\"> 𝐠𝐫𝐚𝐩𝐡𝐢𝐜 𝐯𝐢𝐨𝐥𝐞𝐧𝐜𝐞 </span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 0, 0);\">•</span><span style=\"color: rgb(83, 83, 83);\"> 𝐜𝐫𝐢𝐦𝐞 𝐚𝐜𝐭𝐢𝐯𝐢𝐭𝐢𝐞𝐬 </span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 0, 0);\">•</span><span style=\"color: rgb(83, 83, 83);\"> 𝐨𝐛𝐬𝐞𝐬𝐬𝐢𝐯𝐞 𝐛𝐞𝐡𝐚𝐯𝐢𝐨𝐫 </span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 0, 0);\">•</span><span style=\"color: rgb(83, 83, 83);\"> 𝐬𝐭𝐚𝐥𝐤𝐢𝐧𝐠 </span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 0, 0);\">•</span><span style=\"color: rgb(83, 83, 83);\"> 𝐤𝐢𝐝𝐧𝐚𝐩𝐩𝐢𝐧𝐠&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 0, 0);\">•</span><span style=\"color: rgb(83, 83, 83);\"> 𝐟𝐨𝐫𝐜𝐞𝐝 𝐩𝐫𝐨𝐱𝐢𝐦𝐢𝐭𝐲&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 0, 0);\">•</span><br><br><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://open.spotify.com/playlist/6dZ3qbUpMSAUZedwYpZB6U?si=6a46abad571a4dcc\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(90, 0, 0);\"><strong>➤ＰＬＡＹＬＩＳＴ</strong></span></a></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/VT7DGbpubb1arWA947krX.webp\"></p><p><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/wLv4A5QoL4ZNPBrMmdGFP.webp\"></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><h3 style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 0, 0);\"><strong>ＹＯＵＲ ＳＴＯＲＹ</strong></span></h3><p style=\"text-align: center;\">You're the mafia princess, the cherished daughter of Don Giovanni Vitello. You've lived your life raised in luxury, but for the past four months, you've been risking it all for a secret, passionate affair with Dmitriy Belov - a Russian killer you met at a charity event. One conversation turned into secret meetings, intense and dangerous. Your family found out, and your brother Renato's plan to smuggle you out of New York just went up in flames. Literally.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Now you're standing on a deserted road, watching the car meant to be your escape burn with your guards inside. Dmitriy has an arm wrapped around you, and he's not letting go. He's convinced he's saving you from your family, and he has no intention of ever letting you return.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/VT7DGbpubb1arWA947krX.webp\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 0, 0);\">『</span><span style=\"color: rgb(120, 0, 0);\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(160, 160, 160);\">𝐃𝐌𝐈𝐓𝐑𝐈𝐘 𝐁𝐄𝐋𝐎𝐕</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(84, 0, 0);\">』</span><br><span style=\"color: rgb(160, 160, 160);\">\"𝑆𝑎𝑦 𝑦𝑜𝑢'𝑙𝑙 𝑙𝑜𝑣𝑒 𝑚𝑒 𝑡𝑜 𝑑𝑒𝑎𝑡ℎ, 𝑐𝑎𝑢𝑠𝑒 𝐼 𝑤𝑖𝑙𝑙.\"</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/Zy4N3Egaj_Piu1N3knPMq.gif\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/VT7DGbpubb1arWA947krX.webp\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/rXmYL0JFKZJptKATD5QtI.webp\"></p><p style=\"text-align: 